				<td colspan="2"><span>Its a good idea as a last ditch effort but wouldnt use it as a tactic to count on, the mem wipe portion of the mez is only a 30% chance if i remember correctly. Meaning it just isnt reliable. However i use the mez/mem wipe tactic when solo dogs in PoN, if i get down to the last dog, if its almost full hp and i notice spawn starting again ill just mez it and back away hoping itll mem wipe, it usually works first time every now and then itll take me several tries. 
<br />

<br />
I use it solo but i would never count on it as a tactic that anyone can use. Great info tho. </span></td>
